@NODE "mail_116" " Re: Bitmaps "
From: "DAVID MCMINN (9429210)" <9429210@...>
Date: 11-23-01 10:39:00
Subject: @{b}Re: Bitmaps@{ub}

Hi BenJDvs@...

> Is there any limit on the size and depth of bitmaps in blitz?, or does
it
> depend on the amount of memory?

If you are using any of the blitting commands, then you'll be limited to
OCS sized bitmaps (1024x1024), because they were never updated to use
the big blits of the ECS.


