Date: 11-22-01 01:33:27
Subject: @{b}Re: CD notification again@{ub}

Hi Demon,

> mysignal.l=AllocSignal_(-1)
> If mysignal.l=0

0 is a valid return value. -1 means there was an error.

> od=OpenDevice_(dev$,unit,*ior,0)

&dev$

> *irq\is_Node\ln_Name="CD_CHANGER"

Use a variable and then use &var$

>  *ior\io_Data=&irq

Surely *irq?

> If mp<>0 Then DeleteMsgPort_(myport)

Hmm, surely should be checking the same as the port variable?

> If mysignal>0 Then FreeSignal_(mysignal)

As above, 0 is an OK value. check for >=


