@NODE "mail_173" " Re: GTGetAttrs problem (and greetings to everyone!) "
From: "DAVID MCMINN (9429210)" <9429210@...>
Date: 11-19-01 16:16:45
Subject: @{b}Re: GTGetAttrs problem (and greetings to everyone!)@{ub}

Hi Barnaky

> This part is clear, but when that event is here
> I must be able to recognise if

You can do something like this:

scroller_down.w=0
AddIDCMP #SCROLLER_IDCMP
...
evn.l=WaitEvent
evc.w=EventCode
Select evn
  case #IDCMP_GADGETDOWN
    If GadgetHit=scroller_id
      scroller_down = 1
    EndIf
  case #IDCMP_GADGETUP
    If GadgetHit=scroller_id
      scroller_down = 0
    EndIf
  case #IDCMP_MOUSEMOVE
    If scroller_down=1
      NPrint "New scroller position = ",evc
    EndIf
End Select

---------------------------------------------------------------------
@ENDNODE

