@NODE "mail_192" " Re: Installing AmiBlitz "
From: "DAVID MCMINN (9429210)" <9429210@...>
Date: 11-22-01 10:47:44
Subject: @{b}Re: Installing AmiBlitz@{ub}

> No, you can use the changelib tool which is included in the BBGTLib
fix by
> me, and the BlitzFix archive (fix by Julian Kinraid). There is also a
tool
> on the CD by RWE which does this.

I should have mentioned how to use the changelib tool. The syntax is
'changelib <directory> <libfile>' where <directory> is the directory
that the lib file is in and <libfile> is the library you want to replace
in acidlibs.

I've always found it works best if you change directory to the one with
the lib file and use 'changelib PROGDIR: <libfile>'.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
@ENDNODE

