>

I think that the author does not maked a specific command because you can
read the line then convert to a numeric value by the blitz command Val().
If you have to read a line of a numerical value then do:
value.x=Val(ReadLN(<syntax>))
where .x is the size of the variable and <syntax> is the arguments for the
command (I don't know nor use it).


