Hi Sven

> Sorry for my misunderstanding, but for what situation do you need that
> code ? For getting the (sub)menuitems we have implemented functions?

It's so you can detect multiple menu hits for one #IDCMP_MENUPICK
operation. Try it, hold down RMB and click on a few different menu items
with the LMB (keeping the RMB pressed at all times).

