PT>> Try to use MUINotifyApp xx,#MUIA_String_Acknowledge, #MUIV_EveryTime, xx

Actually, it's:-

MUINotifyApp xx,#MUIA_String_Acknowledge,#MUIV_Everytime,yy

Where xx is the string object number, and yy is the return code. Following code
would be something like:-

ev.l=MUIWaitEvent
If ev=yy
    Do the stuff you want when the enter key is pressed in your string gadget


Regards



Steve
