The original amigalibs.res has much more errors and does not include all the
AmigaOS includes. For example the cd.h, and all the datatypes includes.
You can use the one included in the archive that contains the new commandset
(I don't remeber who is the author nor the name of the archive, but it has
all the libs with an N before the name, e.g. NVWait NWBStartup
NCommandPriority...).

Ciao.


