  Also, AmigaXL comes in the same package as Amithlon, and runs on QNX-
check out the compatibiltity page which lists what programs run and
which don't on the two systems:
  http://amigaosxl.haage-partner.de/frames/software-e.html

 Also AmigaXL can use any device drivers that are supported under QNX
-list of supported devices:
  http://qdn.qnx.com/support/hardware/platform/index.html

  It also, has the benefit of running QNX native apps, like the
Webrowser, which has full Javascript, RealAudio/Video and Flash
support.
   

